ih.kg/1209367</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"72b348fb179f8f8f2b287935e63b284c40235e9d","tid":1678344,"uid":242125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9c39dc6bc36b7a0fa7ccbb7849bdebd7d8f084e0","tid":1678344,"uid":56727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:50:11.000Z","msg":"屌"},{"pid":"984f4f6a3434f775a18efc223afd337ad2964be7","tid":1678344,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:53:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">國際戰線，兩面夾擊！</span></span></strong><br />\n抵抗中國魔掌，需要你課金支持！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>一、遊說戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">中共一直斥巨資，僱用遊說集團在華盛頓進行統戰，收賣美國政客及團體，左右美國政策和輿論。單是華為2019年第3季的遊說支出，就達到176萬美元。董建華的中美交流基金會，過去五年在美國支出近300萬港元。</span><br />\n<strong>組建香港人的遊說團隊，請支持大專學界及香港眾志眾籌計劃！</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港大專學界國際事務代表團眾籌計劃<br />\nHong Kong IAD Crowdfunding Plan</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkiad-crowdfunding%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4TUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=1ecf2f93\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkiad-crowdfunding/</a><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">香港眾志國際眾籌計劃 Demosisto International Campaign Crowdfunding Project</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E7%259C%25BE%25E7%25B1%258C%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project%2F%3Fshow_desktop%3D1&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4TUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=8a27d3eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E7%9C%BE%E7%B1%8C%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-demosisto-international-campaign-crowdfunding-project/?show_desktop=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>二、輿論戰線：</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">香港民主運動和抗爭，不斷受到中國造遙抹黑；中國媒體、英文五毛、投共白人，不斷在網上製造不利香港的輿論。為了令香港人不被代表、為了令外界清楚知道香港清晰的民意；</span><br />\n<strong>香港需要一份科學、具公信力的民調來反映真相。請支持：</strong><br />\n<strong><em><span style=\"color: orange;\">【我們香港人】倡導計劃</span></em></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209%2F&d=qY%2BFdmg29Nq5PZFqoXGv4TUBvjVF43IiJLn9vI4Fxnk%3D&h=158e47f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209/</a>"},{"pid":"c38b60a725d83d3331e186d182dddb57efc4f801","tid":1678344,"uid":107740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:55:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b19da44996d2b3b9e6962b30bf28bbdab73eba62","tid":1678344,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T15:59:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c6f56572b9a5b81245db6cc73d906f6a91fc622","tid":1678344,"uid":28575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:02:35.000Z","msg":"仲唔還拖等幾時, 晚晚街坊落晒黎咁多人圍一隊都係眼定定嗌放人望住手足比班狗帶到人開車走, 你敢還手班狗一定最驚"},{"pid":"3a26a4e8ee3be6ebefdcc3a27571722f9f339711","tid":1678344,"uid":265662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:02:36.000Z","msg":"dllm"},{"pid":"5c5953297e1d86c16d81ab3f51721dd5f7cd0020","tid":1678344,"uid":66049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T16:03:38.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"20f63526d92dc9c2d5f298962361e62efe37fe0c","tid":1678344,"uid":254371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019